text: Veveyse District is a district in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. The capital is Châtel-Saint-Denis. These municipalities are in the district: Coat of Arms Municipality Population (1 Jan. 2004) Area in km² Attalens 2441 9.82 Bossonnens 1153 4.09 Châtel- Saint-Denis 4778 47.90 Granges (Veveyse) 671 4.46 La Verrerie 930 13.42 Le Flon 875 9.54 Remaufens 796 5.89 Saint-Martin 861 8.75 Semsales 1027 29.39
